text:
Price Reduced Country Living! Sitting on 1 Acre 311 Tan ad date: 09/30/2015 
Sitting on 1 Acre 311 Tan Oak Drive, Crescent City, CA Situated in the Hiouchi area, this is the perfect home for the family. 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and 1976 sq ft of living space. It is across the street from the entrance to the Peacock Bar river access. Great swimming and fishing spot. MLS 1500167 $239,500 Kurt Stremberg, Broker 785 E. Washington Blvd #2, Crescent City Office: 707-465-2121 Cell: 707-954-1732
